The following are links to sites that explain the tools and techniques we aim to incorporate into our project

GoogleTest
https://google.github.io/googletest/quickstart-cmake.html
The above link will take you to a page that will help you set up googleTest

https://google.github.io/googletest/primer.html
This link will take you to a page that will introduce to you the basix of using googleTest

Gitflow tutorial
https://www.atlassian.com/git/tutorials/comparing-workflows/gitflow-workflow
Gitflow is the philosophy the Burgundy team aims to use in managing the version control and collaboration in the git envrionment
